name: Uptober
description: UPTOBER is a community token built to celebrate the tradition of “Uptober,” the season of optimism in crypto each fall. Deployed on BNB Chain through the 4Meme platform, it represents the first “Call to Own” (CTO) project recognized from the platform’s experimental launches. The project blends meme culture with accessible decentralized finance, offering a playful yet transparent way for users to participate in on-chain trading, liquidity, and seasonal market culture
